window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ever since I came to Earth, I've been searching for my mentor, Fenton Ashbearer. He broke the rules of magic, and I was given a geas to find him. I'm compelled to hunt him down and bring him to justice.</p> <p>After an encounter with thugs enhanced by magical amulets, I believe I've found him.</p> <p>My old mentor is causing a lot of trouble in my new homeworld. It's going to take all my magical might along with the superpowered heroines of the Offenders to end him.</p>"; 
